INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(2,15,1,'The calm','Ndjdjjdn',NULL,NULL,'2026-03-29 18:18:07','2026-03-29 18:18:07');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(3,16,1,'The Third Bed','Three girls. One dorm room. Adaeze, Chisom, and Amara build an unlikely friendship across every difference the world gave them. Then the scholarship is announced. Nothing survives that unchanged.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-01 07:54:24','2026-04-06 23:21:38');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(4,17,1,'The Prize ',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-01 08:56:37','2026-04-01 08:56:37');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(6,20,2,'The Prize','The competition is inside the room now. Secrets surface, accusations fly, and true things get said in anger. Winning requires becoming someone. The question is who.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-01 11:57:10','2026-04-06 23:22:24');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(8,22,2,'Different Skies: The Reckoning Weeks 7 through 12',replace('\nSeason 2 opens with the shift. Something has changed between the park and Monday morning, and Kemi feels it the way you felt a tooth coming loose: not all at once, just a slow persistent awareness that something fixed was no longer fixed. The friendship is no longer sufficient for what it is carrying. They both know it. Neither of them says it yet.\nThe almost builds across the first two episodes: a phone message late on a Saturday night that opens a door without walking through it, a rain overhang with a shoulder almost touching an arm, a sentence carried to the edge of being spoken and then swallowed when the rain stops and the moment moves. Then the outside world enters with full force: Kemi''s mother calls with a flight date November twenty-eighth, five weeks away, a week before term ends and the abstract twelve becomes a concrete five. The school farewell assembly puts Kemi at the front of the hall writing a speech that cannot be true in public without saying things that belong to the bench. Tobenna''s football season ends and he walks off a field his body has learned and understands he will not return to.\nThe pressure breaks in a fight not a loud one, not a cruel one, but the real kind, the kind that happens when two people are close enough that the unprotected parts of them are touching and the clock is loud and neither of them knows what to do with the feeling except press it toward the other person. Kemi accuses Tobenna of waiting. Tobenna tells her she is managing him the same way she manages everything, that she lets him close enough to matter and then hands him the edited version. She walks away. That night he texts her the truest thing he has managed in weeks, and she texts back: give me until tomorrow.\nTomorrow is the bench. The real conversation, finally. No prepared version, no organised feelings, no careful. Tobenna tells her he is in love with her. Kemi tells him she is in love with him too. Not hedged, not qualified, just said the real size of it, in the harmattan afternoon, with his hand open on the concrete between them and hers placed in it.\nThe final episode is the last day of term. Kemi delivers her speech to the whole school and finds his face in the hall without planning to and keeps her eyes there while she says the true things about choosing distance and refusing to spend limited time being careful of the people who matter. On the bench afterward he gives her a notebook he has been writing in since October observations, things noticed, things he should have said out loud. She gives him back the essay collection, the airport essay, with a line underlined near the end for him to find himself. At the gate where their paths divide they say the words that carry the whole season same uniform, different skies and she walks to her aunt''s car without looking back, not because she is being careful, but because she is being brave, which feels from the inside almost the same and is completely different.\nIn the car, she opens the notebook to the first page. The first line is from the night of the library, the night of the power cut, the night everything started: The lights went out and there was a girl three tables away who didn''t leave.\nShe closes the notebook. She looks at the hills at the edge of the city. She lets herself cry without being careful about it.\nFirst love, the series argues, is not practice. It is not a rehearsal for the real thing. It is the first time you see yourself clearly in the reflection of someone else''s attention, and what you see there changes the shape of every room you walk into after.','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,'2026-04-05 05:23:15','2026-04-05 05:30:37');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(9,23,2,'Different Skies: The Reckoning','The clock is real now. A booked flight, a farewell assembly, a fight that strips the last layer of careful from everything between them. With five weeks left, they finally say the true thing plainly, fully, without hedging. What they carry out of the gate will follow them into different skies.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-06 06:33:04','2026-04-15 23:39:17');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(10,25,1,'The Language Before Words','His grandmother walks into a flood and leaves behind a message no database can decode. Nnamdi follows it into territory the modern world has agreed to forget.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-06 13:03:32','2026-04-06 22:10:48');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(11,26,2,'What the Water Keeps','Nnamdi learns what his grandmother was, what the river is holding, and what his name has meant to both of them since before he was born.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-06 13:29:03','2026-04-06 22:20:55');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(12,27,3,'The Source','The river is waiting. So is his grandmother. Nnamdi must cross the threshold and discover that science and ancestral knowledge were never opposites, just the same river, two banks.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-06 13:43:54','2026-04-06 22:13:34');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(13,28,1,'The Dead Language','Adaora arrives at the sky court cold and watchful. She hears a voice in a forbidden archive speaking a language her grandmother carried to her grave. What begins as thirty dangerous seconds in a dead tongue becomes something neither of them has words for until the war arrives and forces her to choose between what she knows and who she is protecting.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-07 05:29:46','2026-04-07 13:14:13');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(14,29,2,'The Breaking Point','Both of them return changed. The war is reaching its end or its worst shape yet, and their secret is no longer containable. To save the accord they each have to sacrifice something they cannot recover. The dead language gets spoken one final time in a ratification chamber, in front of everyone, in full voice.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-07 05:47:08','2026-04-07 13:18:19');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(16,31,2,'The Reckoning','Seun stops waiting and starts fighting, but every move costs him something. He negotiates with the union boss, confronts Olamide, and learns why his friend took the deal. A hard-earned arrangement gives him sixty days to prove himself. He makes it. Not cleanly. But he makes it.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-08 01:40:18','2026-04-08 09:49:21');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(18,33,2,'THE TRUSTED ONES',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-08 13:28:59','2026-04-08 13:29:19');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(19,34,1,'The Wrong Face in the Mirror',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-08 16:23:54','2026-04-08 16:24:06');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(20,36,1,'The Wrong Face in the Mirror','A name on a birth certificate. A face at a funeral. Seventeen-year-old Emeka Obi begins piecing together a secret his parents have kept his entire life. Season One follows his quiet, solo excavation through documents, silences, and family reunions toward an identity he can feel but cannot yet fully see.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-09 00:02:47','2026-04-09 00:02:57');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(21,37,2,'What the Truth Costs','Emeka knows the truth. Now he has to live inside it. He makes contact with his biological father, forces the full story into the open, and watches his family strain under the weight of it. Season Two asks not who Emeka comes from, but who he chooses to be.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-09 00:27:22','2026-04-09 00:27:31');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(23,39,1,'THE BELT','Emeka runs FGC Lokoja like he built it. Then a new principal introduces elections, a student council, and an eligibility rule that shuts him out completely. The girl who wins by a landslide is Chinazaekpere Hauwa. He punished her for running in a corridor. Now she outranks him.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-09 12:29:45','2026-04-09 12:29:50');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(24,40,1,'The Room',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-09 19:46:05','2026-04-09 19:46:13');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(25,41,2,'THE NEGOTIATION','Emeka resolves to comply coldly. Instead, a food crisis, a hostile teacher, and a borrowed umbrella in the rain pull him into something he has no procedure for. He and Naza stop clashing and start building. Until one tired Wednesday evening, old habits remind both of them how far he still has to go.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-09 21:33:28','2026-04-09 21:34:10');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(26,42,1,'THE DISTANCE BETWEEN SEATS',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-10 00:07:37','2026-04-10 00:07:47');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(27,43,3,'THE REBUILD','The fracture between them is loud. WAEC is coming. Niger House wants a sports result that does not belong to them. And Mrs. Okafor wants a document that forces Emeka and Naza to sit down and write out everything they learned from each other. Some of it is not comfortable.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-10 07:39:42','2026-04-10 07:40:15');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(29,45,1,'Borrowed Joy','Five weddings. Two strangers working the margins of other people''s happiness. Teniola arranges chairs and makes herself small. Kayode carries his father''s drums and his own unspoken ambitions. Across three receptions and the quiet spaces between, they find something real. Then one honest mistake breaks the fragile thing before it has a name.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-10 20:04:35','2026-04-10 20:04:41');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(30,47,2,'Keeping Season','After fourteen days of silence, Teni and Kayode have to decide if what they built can survive being seen. Mothers are watching. Cousins are talking. The last wedding of the season is coming. Before it ends, both of them must face what they have been hiding, including from themselves.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-10 20:23:54','2026-04-10 20:24:02');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(32,49,1,'Dark','Emem visits her sister Afiong in Calabar and sees something on her brother-in-law''s phone she believes is proof of infidelity. She says nothing  then sends screenshots weeks later from a distance. Afiong''s marriage begins to die quietly from the inside. Nobody knows Emem was the one who started it.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-12 13:54:28','2026-04-14 17:13:41');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(33,50,2,'Salt','The families gather and the truth unravels. The screenshots belonged to someone else entirely. The marriage still ends. Afiong goes silent. And Emem must decide who she is going to be inside the wreckage she helped build  not by seeking forgiveness, but by finally choosing truth over self-protection.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-13 02:27:41','2026-04-14 17:22:05');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(34,51,1,'THE PLEDGE BOY','Six-year-old Amaechi arrives at Zara''s royal palace as a political hostage. When the prince makes mistakes, Amaechi takes the punishment. From shared pain comes an unexpected friendship, forged in silence and lamplight. But a senior court adviser sees the bond forming and begins, patiently and precisely, to plan against it.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-14 16:18:32','2026-04-14 16:18:44');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(35,52,2,'THE KING''S OTHER HAND','Now the king''s most trusted attendant, Amaechi is sent north to Kara on a diplomatic mission. He survives a dangerous succession crisis alone, exchanges letters with a king whose health is quietly failing, and rides home as fast as roads allow. He arrives to a closed door and a waiting enemy.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-14 16:48:49','2026-04-14 17:27:18');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(37,53,3,'THE LAND THAT FORGOT HIM','Removed from the palace, Amaechi returns to an Oke that no longer knows him. He finds his mother''s grave and reclaims her promise. He organises resistance, fights with documents and presence, wins small and loses large. He ends in a small room, writing to the boy he once was.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-14 17:41:55','2026-04-14 17:42:09');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(38,54,1,'THE PROMISE','Ivie is sixteen, ambitious, and determined to change her family''s story. When her father''s cousin promises to take her to Italy after her O-levels, she studies harder than she has ever studied for anything. She earns everything the deal requires. She boards the plane. She walks into the wrong house.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-15 07:04:30','2026-04-15 20:40:53');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(39,55,2,'THE CAGE','Madam names the debt. It is designed to be impossible. Ivie decides it is a problem with a solution. While her body works off what she owes, her mind builds something no one in that building can enter or take. She runs two sets of numbers. Hers reaches zero first.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-15 07:18:40','2026-04-15 20:41:52');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(40,56,3,'NEW GROUND','New York is enormous and indifferent and occasionally, unexpectedly, kind. Ivie finds work, a room, a classroom, and a man named Tunde who does not flinch at the full story. When Aunty Osato is arrested and jailed, grief and relief arrive together. Neither surprises her. She was ready for both.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-15 07:31:16','2026-04-15 20:44:17');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(41,58,1,'The Quiet Man','The offer arrives at exactly the wrong time. With routes closing and money thinning, Osaro and Idemudia take a job from a stranger who knows too much and asks too little. One delivery becomes three. The cousins stop speaking the same language. When Idemudia goes alone on the final run, the road takes something it does not return.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-18 06:16:12','2026-04-18 06:16:12');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(42,59,2,'Which Road','Idemudia is missing. The quiet man has a name and a history that runs through their uncle''s past. Osaro walks into the network his cousin chose and finds a way out, but the exit costs everything he saved. When the road finally clears, both cousins are free. Just not together.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-18 06:31:59','2026-04-18 06:32:10');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(43,66,1,'The World That Was','Adanna Obi is sixteen and untouchable a girl built from the right school, the right address, the right friends. When her father''s company is seized by government authorities, her world collapses with a speed that teaches her everything about what she had. Her friends disappear. The compound empties. As her family prepares to cross from Lagos Island to Mushin, Adanna watches the only version of herself she has ever known being packed into boxes and realizes she has no idea what lies underneath.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-20 10:40:30','2026-04-20 10:40:40');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(44,67,2,'The World as It Is','Mushin is loud, close, and completely fluent in a language Adanna does not speak. Her new school does not know the hierarchy she arrived holding, and Chinedu, her quietly perceptive guide, refuses to be impressed by the girl she is performing. Through shared textbooks, rain-soaked roads, and arguments about Soyinka, something real begins to grow between them. But Adanna cannot love him until she grieves herself first the girl she was, the life that was borrowed, and the identity she must now build from what actually holds.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-20 10:44:43','2026-04-20 10:44:53');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(45,61,1,'What She Carried','Chiamaka arrives at Queen''s Hallmark Secondary School in Ibadan with her Lagos identity as her only remaining asset. Placed in the bottom bunk beneath a girl who already knows her family''s scandal, she spends one brutal term performing a life she no longer has. As hunger, academic panic, and hostel politics strip away her armor, a careless betrayal fractures the room and leaves her facing the question she has been running from since September: who is she without the performance?',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-20 12:08:02','2026-04-20 12:08:21');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(46,62,2,'What She Builds','With her armor gone and the room fractured, Chiamaka must figure out who she actually is. As a familiar face from her Lagos life arrives to pull her backward, a quiet girl opens a notebook, a housemother offers unexpected truth, and a rain-soaked afternoon begins to crack open the wall between her and Temi. In a term defined by what things cost to fix, Chiamaka learns that belonging is not conquered but earned, slowly, through honesty, and through the willingness to stay in the room.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-20 12:09:36','2026-04-20 12:09:41');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(47,68,1,'Frequency','Chisom has always been more herself when no one is watching. Khalil talks the way most people write. Paired in an inter-school exchange program, their first voice notes are stilted and polite. By the fifth exchange something shifts. By the tenth they are telling each other things they have told no one else. Season 1 follows the building of a private world, one voice note at a time, as Chisom falls in love with a laugh she has never seen.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-20 18:55:44','2026-05-30 10:07:33');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(48,70,1,'THE DREAMING','When construction trucks arrive at Agulu Lake, sixteen-year-old Oby begins dreaming in her ancestor''s voice. She wakes knowing impossible things, about the lake''s depth, her bloodline''s sacred role, and seven stones buried beneath the water. As machines inch closer and a community vote fails her, Oby realises the inheritance she never asked for cannot be returned.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-20 20:15:59','2026-04-20 20:16:10');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(49,71,2,'THE WAKING','The excavation begins and the lake fights back. Wells run dry, water rises, crocodiles come ashore. Oby builds an unlikely team and uncovers a colonial document that illegally erased the lake''s sacred status. But the buried covenant is fracturing fast and the legal process is too slow. Oby makes a decision only she can make.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-21 20:11:53','2026-04-21 20:12:03');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(50,72,3,'THE REMEMBERING','Oby surfaces from the lake changed, carrying knowledge that stops the construction legally and permanently. But the covenant must still be renewed before the seal breaks completely. With her mother finally stepping into her own inheritance beside her, Oby descends one last time to finish what her ancestor began in 1897 and remake what her line almost lost.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-21 20:25:55','2026-04-21 20:26:07');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(51,76,1,'CAUGHT ','For four months, Simi has observed a boy on her morning danfo from a careful distance. She knows everything about him except his name. When their bus breaks down on Carter Bridge and they end up in the same queue at the principal''s office, the distance collapses in four words she did not mean to say: I know. Season 1 follows the slow, embarrassing, electric process of being caught being yourself by someone who was already paying attention, and finding out they were doing the same thing.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-29 02:26:57','2026-04-29 02:27:05');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(52,77,2,'KNOWN ','Femi moves one seat closer on the danfo and the whole bus notices before either of them says it out loud. Season 2 takes Simi and Femi outside the route, into a park in Surulere, into her quiet house in the evenings, into the first real argument that is not about being wrong but about being seen too accurately. What begins to crack between them is not the connection but the last wall around it, and choosing to take it down is the bravest thing either of them does all year.',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-29 02:43:51','2026-04-29 02:44:11');
INSERT INTO "seasons" ("id","novel_id","season_number","title","synopsis","cover_image_url","release_date","created_at","updated_at") VALUES(53,69,2,'Proof','When an inter-school visit is announced, the relationship that Chisom and Khalil built in the safety of voice notes must face the one thing it was never designed for a room. Season 2 follows both of them walking toward the visit with their fears fully named, their feelings fully admitted, and everything they built about to be tested. The finale does not flinch. It earns whatever it finds, and finds something true.',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-30 09:44:22','2026-05-30 09:45:16');
